A video trending on social media shows Kogi state governor, Yahaya Bello working out in other to keep fit. The Kogi state governor is well know to love fitness training and exercise, and we can recall that last year he went viral while boxing ahead of his reelection. In the new video, he can be seen sweating out to stay fit and perhaps, keep himself ready in self-defense. Watch the video below; Governor Yahaya Bello of Kogi state keeping fit pic.twitter.com/WlE9ujelHb Source